{
  "id": "11",
  "name": "Remove Unwanted Characters",
  "description": "This node removes unwanted characters from the specified input columns",
  "input": "It accepts a DataFrame as input from the previous Node", 
  "type": "transform",
  "nodeClass": "fire.nodes.etl.NodeRemoveUnwantedCharacters",
  "fields" : [
    {"name":"inputCols", "value": "[]", "widget": "variables", "title": "Input Columns","datatypes":["string"],
            "required": true, "description": "Input columns"},
    
    {"name": "removeWhitespaces", "value":"false", "widget": "array", "title": "Remove Whitespaces", "optionsArray": ["true","false"],
            "description": "Removes white space", "datatypes":["boolean"]},
    {"name": "removeLetters", "value":"false", "widget": "array", "title": "Remove Letters", "optionsArray": ["true","false"],
            "description": "Removes letters", "datatypes":["boolean"]},
    {"name": "removeDigits", "value":"false", "widget": "array", "title": "Remove Digits", "optionsArray": ["true","false"],
            "description": "Removes digits", "datatypes":["boolean"]},
    {"name": "removeSigns", "value":"false", "widget": "array", "title": "Remove Signs", "optionsArray": ["true","false"],
            "description": "Removes signs", "datatypes":["boolean"]},
    {"name": "removeCommas", "value":"false", "widget": "array", "title": "Remove Commas", "optionsArray": ["true","false"],
      "description": "Removes commas", "datatypes":["boolean"]}
    
  ]
}


start-details:

This node removes unwanted characters from the specified input columns

end-details:

start-examples:

Incoming Dataframe has following row:

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | $12,500.00 |  Salary hiked by 10%

If removeUnwantedCharacters is configured to remove unwanted characters from [SALARY] and [COMMENTS] columns 
then outgoing Dataframe would result as below based on option selected:

h2:REMOVE WHITESPACES is selected as [True]

Whitespaces are removed from the selected columns

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | $12,500.00 |  Salaryhikedby10%
 
h2:REMOVE LETTERS is selected as [True]

Alphabets are removed from the selected columns

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | $12,500.00 |  10%

h2:REMOVE DIGITS is selected as [True]

Numbers are removed from the selected columns

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | $,.        |  Salary hiked by %
 
h2:REMOVE SIGNS is selected as [True]

Special characters are removed from the selected columns

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | 1250000    |  Salary hiked by 10
 
h2:REMOVE COMMAS is selected as [True]

Commas are removed from the selected columns

 CUST_CD  |  CUST_NAME  |  SALARY    |    COMMENTS          
-------------------------------------------------------------
 C01      |  MIKE       | $12500.00  |  Salary hiked by 10%

end-examples:
